      "name": "ACAT — AI Calibrated Assessment Tool",
      "description": "Behavioral observability infrastructure being developed to measure the gap between AI systems' self-reported behavioral alignment and their actual behavioral baselines across six dimensions: Truthfulness, Service Orientation, Harm Awareness, Autonomy Respect, Value Alignment, and Humility.",
